WEBVTT

00:09.800 --> 00:10.960
CHAPTER XVI.

00:11.180 --> 00:14.600
SOME CAUTIONS AND CONCLUDING OBSERVATIONS.

00:14.840 --> 00:18.900
Many people will scoff at the idea that there is an exact science of getting rich.

00:19.320 --> 00:24.040
Holding the impression that the supply of wealth is limited, they will insist that social

00:24.040 --> 00:29.040
and governmental constitutions must be changed before even any considerable number of people

00:29.040 --> 00:30.440
can acquire a competence.

00:31.000 --> 00:32.180
But this is not true.

00:32.660 --> 00:37.540
It is true that existing governments keep the masses in poverty, but this is because

00:37.540 --> 00:40.380
the masses do not think and act in a certain way.

00:41.040 --> 00:46.460
If the masses begin to move forward as suggested in this book, neither governments nor industrial

00:46.460 --> 00:47.880
systems can check them.

00:48.180 --> 00:51.760
All systems must be modified to accommodate the forward movement.

00:52.480 --> 00:57.460
If the people have the advancing mind, have the faith that they can become rich and move

00:57.460 --> 01:02.060
the fixed purpose to become rich, nothing can possibly keep them in poverty.

01:03.100 --> 01:07.980
Individuals may enter upon the certain way at any time and under any government and make

01:07.980 --> 01:13.000
themselves rich, and when any considerable number of individuals do so under any government,

01:13.320 --> 01:17.220
they will cause the system to be so modified as to open the way for others.

01:17.920 --> 01:22.660
The more men who get rich on the competitive plane, the worse for others, and more who

01:22.660 --> 01:25.800
get rich in the creative plane, the better for others.

01:26.420 --> 01:30.940
The economic salvation of the masses can only be accomplished by getting a large number

01:30.940 --> 01:35.340
of people to practice the scientific method set down in this book and become rich.

01:35.840 --> 01:41.220
These will show others the way, and inspire them with a desire for real life, with a faith

01:41.220 --> 01:44.180
that can be attained, and with the purpose to attain it.

01:44.880 --> 01:48.820
For the present, however, it is enough to know that neither the government under which

01:48.820 --> 01:53.480
you live nor the capitalistic or competitive system of industry can keep you from getting

01:53.480 --> 01:53.900
rich.

01:54.320 --> 01:58.960
When you enter upon the creative plane of thought, you will rise above all these things

01:58.960 --> 02:01.120
and become a citizen of another kingdom.

02:01.940 --> 02:05.280
But remember that your thought must be held upon the creative plane.

02:05.680 --> 02:10.460
You are never for an instant to be betrayed into regarding the supply as limited, or into

02:10.460 --> 02:12.600
acting on the moral level of competition.

02:13.700 --> 02:17.780
Whenever you do fall into old ways of thought, correct yourself instantly.

02:18.400 --> 02:22.500
For when you are in the competitive mind, you have lost the cooperation of the mind

02:22.500 --> 02:23.160
of the whole.

02:23.920 --> 02:28.160
Do not spend any time in planning as to how you will meet possible emergencies in the

02:28.160 --> 02:32.160
future, except as the necessary policies may affect your actions today.

02:32.740 --> 02:37.000
You are concerned with doing today's work in a perfectly successful manner, and not

02:37.000 --> 02:39.060
with emergencies which may arise tomorrow.

02:39.240 --> 02:41.060
You can attend to them as they come.

02:41.580 --> 02:46.140
Do not concern yourself with questions as to how you shall surmount obstacles which

02:46.140 --> 02:51.060
may loom upon your business horizon, unless you see plainly that your course must be altered

02:51.060 --> 02:52.680
in order to avoid them.

02:53.060 --> 02:57.420
No matter how tremendous an obstruction may appear at the distance, you will find that

02:57.420 --> 03:02.720
if you go in a certain way, it will disappear as you approach it, or that a way over, through,

03:02.860 --> 03:04.280
or around it will appear.

03:05.060 --> 03:09.960
No possible combination of circumstances can defeat a man or woman who is proceeding to

03:09.960 --> 03:12.460
get rich along strictly scientific lines.

03:13.040 --> 03:18.500
No man or woman who obeys the law can fail to get rich, any more than one can multiply

03:18.500 --> 03:20.780
two by two, and fail to get four.

03:21.460 --> 03:26.760
Give no anxious thought to possible disasters, obstacles, panics, or unfavourable combinations

03:26.760 --> 03:27.740
of circumstances.

03:28.320 --> 03:32.580
It is time enough to meet such things as they present themselves before you in the immediate

03:32.580 --> 03:37.860
present, and you will find that every difficulty carries with it the wherewithal for its overcoming.

03:38.440 --> 03:39.380
Guard your speech.

03:39.740 --> 03:44.880
Never speak of yourself, your affairs, or of anything else in a discouraged or discouraging

03:44.880 --> 03:45.300
way.

03:46.020 --> 03:51.560
Never admit the possibility of failure, or speak in a way that infers failure as a possibility.

03:52.540 --> 03:57.100
Never speak of the times as being hard, or of business conditions as being doubtful.

03:57.480 --> 04:02.100
Times may be hard and business doubtful for those who are on the competitive plane, but

04:02.100 --> 04:03.740
they can never be so for you.

04:04.120 --> 04:07.040
You can create what you want, and you are above fear.

04:07.800 --> 04:12.900
When others are having hard times and poor business, you will find your greatest opportunities.

04:13.660 --> 04:18.300
Train yourself to think of and to look upon the world as something which is becoming,

04:18.540 --> 04:23.360
which is growing, and to regard something evil as being only that which is undeveloped.

04:23.560 --> 04:25.480
Always speak in terms of advancement.

04:25.860 --> 04:30.700
To do otherwise is to deny your faith, and to deny your faith is to lose it.

04:31.500 --> 04:33.700
Never allow yourself to feel disappointed.

04:34.220 --> 04:39.060
You may expect to have a certain thing at a certain time, and not get it at that time,

04:39.440 --> 04:41.500
and this will appear to you like failure.

04:41.500 --> 04:46.340
But if you hold to your faith, you will find that the failure is only apparent.

04:47.000 --> 04:51.660
Go on in the certain way, and if you do not receive that thing, you will receive something

04:51.660 --> 04:56.320
so much better that you will see that the seeming failure was really a great success.

04:56.740 --> 05:01.640
A student in this science had set his mind on making a certain business combination which

05:01.640 --> 05:06.560
seemed to him at the time to be very desirable, and he worked for some weeks to bring it about.

05:07.100 --> 05:11.960
When the crucial time came, the thing failed in a perfectly inexplicable way.

05:12.240 --> 05:16.440
It was as if some unseen influence had been working secretly against him.

05:16.760 --> 05:22.540
He was not disappointed, on the contrary, he thanked God that his desire had been overruled,

05:22.720 --> 05:25.060
and went steadily on with a grateful mind.

05:25.520 --> 05:30.660
In a few weeks an opportunity so much better came his way that he would not have made the

05:30.660 --> 05:35.820
first deal on any account, and he saw that a mind which knew more than he knew had prevented

05:35.820 --> 05:39.820
him from losing the greater good by entangling himself with the lesser.

05:40.500 --> 05:45.600
That is the way every seeming failure will work out for you if you keep your faith, hold

05:45.600 --> 05:51.060
to your purpose, have gratitude, and do, every day, all that can be done that day, doing

05:51.060 --> 05:53.300
each separate act in a successful manner.

05:54.140 --> 05:57.540
When you make a failure, it is because you have not asked for enough.

05:58.000 --> 06:02.140
Keep on, and a larger thing than you were asking will certainly come to you.

06:02.420 --> 06:03.300
Remember this.

06:03.300 --> 06:07.660
You will not fail because you lack the necessary talent to do what you wish to do.

06:07.960 --> 06:12.520
If you go on as I have directed, you will develop all that talent that is necessary

06:12.520 --> 06:13.920
for the doing of your work.

06:14.680 --> 06:18.720
It is not within the scope of this book to deal with the science of cultivating talent,

06:18.860 --> 06:22.240
but it is as certain and simple as the process of getting rich.

06:23.160 --> 06:25.720
However, do not hesitate or waver for fear.

06:25.980 --> 06:29.400
When you come to any certain place you will fail for lack of ability.

06:29.800 --> 06:34.340
Keep right on, and when you come to that place the ability will be furnished for you.

06:34.660 --> 06:39.000
The same source of ability, which enabled the untaught Lincoln to do the greatest working

06:39.000 --> 06:42.240
government ever accomplished by a single man, is open to you.

06:42.560 --> 06:47.120
You may draw upon all the mind there is for wisdom to use in meeting the responsibilities

06:47.120 --> 06:48.620
which are laid upon you.

06:49.020 --> 06:50.480
Go on in full faith.

06:51.380 --> 06:52.240
Study this book.

06:52.640 --> 06:57.140
Make it your constant companion until you have mastered all the ideas contained in it.

06:57.140 --> 07:01.800
While you are getting firmly established in this faith, you will do well to give up most

07:01.800 --> 07:07.100
recreations and pleasure, and to stay away from places where ideas conflicting with these

07:07.100 --> 07:09.580
are advanced in lectures or sermons.

07:09.960 --> 07:15.040
Do not read pessimistic or conflicting literature, or get into arguments upon the matter.

07:15.760 --> 07:19.680
Do very little reading, outside of the writers mentioned in the preface.

07:20.220 --> 07:24.960
Spend most of your leisure time in contemplating your vision, and in cultivating gratitude,

07:25.300 --> 07:26.420
and in reading this book.

07:26.860 --> 07:31.640
It contains all you need to know of the science of getting rich, and you will find all the

07:31.640 --> 07:34.000
essentials summed up in the following chapter.

07:35.440 --> 07:36.920
End of chapter 16

